Add list and add to list functions
Add mark and unmark function and implement classes
commitResults.messageBody:
The main program is handling all functionalities. This includes
related behaviors.

The related behaviors can be encapsulated in a class which also reduces
code clutter

We should group the related functions of the task list and the task into
it's own classes.

This allows for better modularity of the code for future purposes and
also reduces code clutter.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add deadline, event and todo tasks and inheritance
commitResults.messageBody:
Task classes (e.g. DeadlineTask, EventTask etc.) have some common
behaviors with each other.

The common behaviors are causing duplication of code.

We can extract the similar behaviors into a superclass Task to support
polymorphism as well as reduce code duplication.

Let us create a superclass Task that the other tasks like deadlines and
events inherit from.
